sentences.sentence: You have carried it with you in successive incarnations, albeit in your subconsciousness.
sentences.translation: 你们在前世已经携带它，在你的潜意识中。

sentences.sentence: Their attachment to men will be characterized as self-disvalue from their subjective subconsciousness.
sentences.translation: 自轻自贱是女性依附男人的主观潜意识表征；

sentences.sentence: Every cell, body tissue, bone and tendon of your whole body is under the control of your subconsciousness.
sentences.translation: 你全身的每个细胞和身体组织，每根骨骼和肌腱，每个器官和肌肉都是受你的潜意识的控制。
